PASTE_YOUR_APH_AUTH_COOKIE_VALUE_HERE

To get your cookie:
1. Go to https://www.aphistoryforge.com/guide/
2. Open DevTools (F12) → Application → Cookies → aphistoryforge.com
3. Copy the value of 'aph_auth' (the long JWT token)
4. Paste it here and save as 'austin_way_auth.txt' (remove this example text)
